long-description.p: Heavy muggle presence in the area, so try to decide on your course of action in advance!
The proximity of trees and buildings may lead to poor satellite reception, so you should wander up and down the pavement observing the environment!

2010-06-12T19:00:00Z : Didn't find it by zo0g
We had a few problems with this one. there were SO many people around that it made it difficult to search. Also, the GPS was having a hard time getting signals. Anyhow, besides all the excuses, we missed it. The park was beautiful though! thanks.

Found in the the hands of other cachers. Nice and easy!
